# Planning Rule

When work is non-trivial, produce a short plan with:
- Objective
- Scope (in/out)
- Ordered execution steps
- Risks/dependencies
- Verification strategy

## Execution Discipline
- Keep exactly one step actively in progress.
- Update plan when scope changes.
- Capture assumptions explicitly and convert unresolved items into TODOs in brain files.
